casebody.data:
Chau Kieu NGUYEN, as Representative of Dung Kim Nguyen, and the Estate of Luong Trung Nguyen, petitioner,
v.
JP MORGAN CHASE BANK, NA. No. 12-1382. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 709 F.3d 1342 . Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied. Justice ALITO took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
